{"id":146898,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/警方冲入格尔登寺-两名藏人身亡/","date":"2011-04-23T11:30:17Z","modified":"2011-04-23T11:30:17Z","title":"警方冲入格尔登寺 两名藏人身亡","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据法新社报道，</span>4<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span>21<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日夜间，四川省阿坝县格尔登寺的局势急转直下。当局派出军警冲入寺庙，</span>300<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">余名僧侣被警方带走。法新社援引“国际声援西藏组织”的消息称，在行动中，守护在寺庙门前的藏民遭到军警殴打，其中两名年逾</span>60<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的信徒不幸身亡，另有多人受伤。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社事发后尝试联系四川阿坝警方，但当局不愿透露有关此事的任何消息。当地居民也不愿就此接受采访。而新华社</span>22<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日则称，因部分僧侣的违法行为，阿坝县当局已于近日开展一场“法制教育活动”。近期格尔登寺局势紧张的起因是</span>3<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月中旬，一名僧侣自焚身亡后，遗体被运入格尔登寺。中国官方认为，这起自焚事件是一场“精心策划的暴乱”。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15025579%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%86%B2%E5%85%A5%E6%A0%BC%E5%B0%94%E7%99%BB%E5%AF%BA+%E4%B8%A4%E5%90%8D%E8%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=752465\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"